					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">That's only for the bytecode. The BASIC dialect will be the classic 8-bit BASIC which was ubiquitous in the 80s. The plan is to transform the BASIC listing into something the interpreter in the NES can process as fast as possible. Tokenized listings, easy to digest expresions, precalculated jumps, etc.</div>

					
